data.title: Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna and Princess Irina Alexandrovna
data.meta_description: Photograph of Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna (1875-1960) and Princess Irina Alexandrovna (1895-1970). Grand Duchess Xenia is wearing a blouse with full sleeves and a striped pattern and is holding the baby Princess Irina on her knee. The photograph is signed Xenia.Grand Duchess Xenia Alexandrovna was the eldest daughter of Alexander III, Emperor of Russia and his consort Maria Feodorovna.
